<JadeInterface name="IF_VoyageMovemt" id="bbdad2a8-8274-40d7-bbb1-2c8b486ffcc8">
    <text>DH - 28/3/2008
The HMS_VoyageMovement object and the CMIF_HMS_WorkingMovement Object
have replicated code in many places in the system, which makes maintenance 
very difficult.  This interface has been created in the hope that 
it can be used to allow these classes to share code. 
 
</text>
    <JadeInterfaceMethod name="isArrival" id="cfb6b60c-4e28-450f-afa0-d19c86eeca3b">
        <source>isArrival():Boolean;</source>
        <ReturnType type="Boolean"/>
    </JadeInterfaceMethod>
    <JadeInterfaceMethod name="isDeparture" id="6dbe5664-4e45-4c65-9046-00fee68ea606">
        <source>isDeparture():Boolean;</source>
        <ReturnType type="Boolean"/>
    </JadeInterfaceMethod>
    <JadeInterfaceMethod name="isFromSameVoyageAs" id="43c01280-1b77-49e0-96be-9122efe9819a">
        <source>isFromSameVoyageAs(move : Object):Boolean;</source>
        <Parameter name="move" type="Object"/>
        <ReturnType type="Boolean"/>
    </JadeInterfaceMethod>
</JadeInterface>
